{"id":64426,"title":"Biologics in systemic lupus erythematosus: current options and future perspectives.","abstract":"Data from clinical trials highlighted the potential and pitfalls of the use of biologics to treat systemic lupus erythematosus. With improved understanding of immunopathogenesis and lessons learned from controlled trials, there is a growing optimism for personalized treatment from an increasing range of targeted therapies. ","date":"2014-08-12","categories":"Immune System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25111095","annotations":[{"name":"Systemic lupus erythematosus","weight":0.889548,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Systemic_lupus_erythematosus"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Systemic disease","weight":0.783517,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Systemic_disease"},{"name":"Clinical trial","weight":0.748217,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_trial"},{"name":"Biologic","weight":0.602943,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biologic"},{"name":"Targeted therapy","weight":0.344669,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Targeted_therapy"},{"name":"Lupus erythematosus","weight":0.0818048,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lupus_erythematosus"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"Option (finance)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Option_(finance)"},{"name":"Optimism","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optimism"},{"name":"Personalized medicine","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personalized_medicine"},{"name":"Data","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data"}]}
